    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Mind
---
The mind is an instrument for communication, for practical purposes. The
mind cannot grasp the truth. The Self witnesses the mind, but the mind
cannot catch hold of the Self. ...The mind can only work with some name or
form or image. If you give this up, the mind will be helpless.
